title: 164. Realizing Unrealized Potential Through Duty
itunes:title: 164. Realizing Unrealized Potential Through Duty
description: It's your obligation as an American to fulfill your true potential. In today's episode, Andy talks about the responsibility citizens have to America, how real noticeable change happens on the ground level, and the actions you can take to make that change happen now.
